-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtl1665702651098.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtl1665702651098.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtl1665702651098.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614007\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614007\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jtl1665702651098.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jtl1665702651098.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jtl1665702651098.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jtl1665702651098\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Toolbar\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Displays a toolbar for the widget, containing the specified items.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__p_d108221e1_d108222e1_d108223e1\">toolbar<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">attribute</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n        {<code class=\"ph codeph\">font</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">indentation</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n        {<code class=\"ph codeph\">bulletlist</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n        {<code class=\"ph codeph\">alignment</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">textcolor</code>}</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__section_ryb_dff_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d836796e93\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__p_d108227e1_d108228e1_d108229e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Toolbar</span> property contains a\n        comma-delimited string of toolbar properties that determine the tools that are included in\n        the toolbar. The order of these properties determines the order in which they are displayed\n        in the toolbar.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Valid Toolbar Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Toolbar Icons</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">attribute</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Displays the Bold, Italic, and Underline buttons.</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__fig_mzj_2ff_1xb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__image_t41_gff_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtfedit_fontattribute.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">font</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Displays the Font Name and Font Size controls</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The contents Font Name list depends on the fonts installed under Microsoft\n                  Windows.</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__fig_qzj_2ff_1xb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" aria-label=\"Open image in gallery mode\" class=\"image expandable\" data-fancy=\"gallery\" data-gallery=\"gallery\" data-remote=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtfedit_font.png?_LANG=enus\" data-title=\"\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__image_oh5_hff_1xb\" role=\"button\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtfedit_font.png?_LANG=enus\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" tabindex=\"0\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">indentation</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Displays the Indent Text and Outdent Text buttons</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__fig_tzj_2ff_1xb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__image_wrc_jff_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtfedit_indentation.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">bulletlist</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Displays the Bulleted List button</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__fig_xzj_2ff_1xb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__image_dmb_lff_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtfedit_bulletlist.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">alignment</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Displays the Left Align, Right Align, and Center Align buttons.</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__fig_a1k_2ff_1xb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__image_pzj_mff_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtfedit_align.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">textcolor</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Displays the Text Color button</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jtl1665702651098__table_d12755e1_d12756e1_d12757e1__entry__3\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__fig_d1k_2ff_1xb\">\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__image_pky_nff_1xb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtfedit_textcolor.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__p_d108230e1_d108231e1_d108232e1\">It is not possible to specify individual controls in\n        the toolbar. For example, you cannot display only the Bold and Italic controls and not\n        display the Underline button. If you specify <code class=\"ph codeph\">attribute</code> in the\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Toolbar</span>, all three buttons are displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__p_d108233e1_d108234e1_d108235e1\">The toolbar color is determined by the  PANELCOLOR setting in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span>\n        file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__p_d108236e1_d108237e1_d108238e1\">This is a static property that cannot be set in\n        ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__section_ev4_pff_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d836796e370\">Example: Setting in the Initialization File</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__p_d108242e1_d108243e1_d108244e1\">For example, to include a complete toolbar in the\n        widget you can set the property as:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__pre_ulh_rff_1xb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">RichEditBox=urtfeditbox(font=editfont;dimmedbackcolor=off;toolbar=attribute,font,indentation,bulletlist,alignment,textcolor)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jtl1665702651098__section_hgl_rff_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d836796e382\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qwk1688451210612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qwk1688451210612.html\" title=\"The urtfeditbox widget is used to display and edit text as Rich Text Format (RTF), which supports formatting such as font and color attributes, text alignment, indentation, and lists. Uniface provides a logical widget called RichEditBox, which is mapped to urtfeditbox.\">urtfeditbox (RichEditBox)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fbn1665702616587.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PanelColor</a><p>Determines the background color of panels.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614007\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614007\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Toolbar Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Toolbar Displays a toolbar for the widget, containing the specified items. toolbar = { attribute } , { font } , { indentation } , { bulletlist } , { alignment } , { textcolor } Description The Toolbar property contains a comma-delimited string of toolbar properties that determine the tools that are included in the toolbar. The order of these properties determines the order in which they are displayed in the toolbar. Table 1. Valid Toolbar Properties Property Description Toolbar Icons attribute Displays the Bold, Italic, and Underline buttons. font Displays the Font Name and Font Size controls The contents Font Name list depends on the fonts installed under Microsoft Windows. indentation Displays the Indent Text and Outdent Text buttons bulletlist Displays the Bulleted List button alignment Displays the Left Align, Right Align, and Center Align buttons. textcolor Displays the Text Color button It is not possible to specify individual controls in the toolbar. For example, you cannot display only the Bold and Italic controls and not display the Underline button. If you specify attribute in the Toolbar , all three buttons are displayed. The toolbar color is determined by the PANELCOLOR setting in the .ini file. This is a static property that cannot be set in ProcScript. Example: Setting in the Initialization File For example, to include a complete toolbar in the widget you can set the property as: RichEditBox=urtfeditbox(font=editfont;dimmedbackcolor=off;toolbar=attribute,font,indentation,bulletlist,alignment,textcolor) Copy Applies To urtfeditbox (RichEditBox) Related Links PanelColor Determines the background color of panels. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}